Ecological notes : very common in broad-leaved, mixed and carr woodland; wet and dry heathland; wetlands including water meadows, fens, bogs, basin mires, sedge beds and
Cladium
beds with tufa; former gravel workings; grassland with pingo pools; old hedges; gardens; around rotten fallen tree trunk; coastal landslip. iv–x.
